{
  "id": "RAW_ea630d",
  "title": "GPT-4o 的多模态生图，让整个设计圈都开始 emo 了。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/wbrIxyJIrf_c4emK6mdnwg",
  "date": "2025-03-27 19:12:23",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GPT4o的多模态生图前天上线之后。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">经过两天的发酵，含金量还在不断提升。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在我的群里，已经能看到越来越多的，进入到实际生产环节的例子。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">@银海</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的直接做商品图的翻译和合成，这是原来的算法，很难做的效果，但是现在，有手就行。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ce4d35c-ed14-4f2f-8d04-8b19aef98300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.8680981595092025\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1304\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186320\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ce4d35c-ed14-4f2f-8d04-8b19aef98300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">非常复杂的电商流程，一张原始图，换产品换脸换衣服。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e216ac88-8728-40d9-ecc8-40a84172f400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9975155279503105\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"805\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186321\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e216ac88-8728-40d9-ecc8-40a84172f400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">@</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">歸藏</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的直接把UI图放样机里面的例子，如果做过UI或者产品设计的朋友肯定都知道，以前我们在做做展示，或者做汇报的时候，经常做样机做的挺痛苦的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c2612ee8-8549-465b-eb8a-163ade400800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7263705103969754\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2116\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186317\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c2612ee8-8549-465b-eb8a-163ade400800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如给他头像，画的两套表情包，是可以直接上架到微信表情商店的那种。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1a57bc0b-c5d0-4f73-f231-3163e574d000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186318\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1a57bc0b-c5d0-4f73-f231-3163e574d000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9a1ff7cb-79f2-4e8b-ea61-107e374d3100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2048\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186319\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9a1ff7cb-79f2-4e8b-ea61-107e374d3100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">来自设计大佬</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">@付遥</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，用GPT-4o来直接做之前非常流行的3D品牌海报。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ef7a17bd-a709-4826-87b2-1b83ffb41600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0249307479224377\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1083\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186323\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ef7a17bd-a709-4826-87b2-1b83ffb41600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我一个很喜欢的小红书AI博主</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">@</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">Rico有三猫</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，用GPT-4o给她做小红书封面。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/13417e0b-5696-4134-c9c5-ac627cb41f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.9617977528089887\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1335\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186325\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/13417e0b-5696-4134-c9c5-ac627cb41f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也用GPT-4o直接做商品图翻译出海。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">群友</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">@</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">默月佥</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在用GPT-4o出蜜蜂的解剖科普图。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ef3b374d-788e-456c-7cc2-380483542a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.930870083432658\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"839\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186326\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ef3b374d-788e-456c-7cc2-380483542a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个很专业的公众号AI博主</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">@</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">阿真lrene</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，不仅用GPT-4o生成复杂的漫画，还能抠图，一键直出透明通道的PNG图。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/128c425d-6d9f-414b-6cc3-0e5a810c0b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2531645569620253\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"790\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186333\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/128c425d-6d9f-414b-6cc3-0e5a810c0b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">干死各种抠图软件的不是更牛逼的抠图软件，而是大模型。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有朋友</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">@</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">不知名网友虎子哥</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，用GPT-4o给他自己家的房子装修。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a1330956-0529-4154-7366-9d70a1b5e300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186327\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a1330956-0529-4154-7366-9d70a1b5e300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有一些我确实不知道源头的但是被传播的蛮广的例子（如有作者，欢迎评论区认领）。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给几个家具做一个展示图，这个场景在电商领域无敌。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd4b51ca-e12f-4890-ef6d-c29e2662d700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0600961538461537\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"832\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186324\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd4b51ca-e12f-4890-ef6d-c29e2662d700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之前我写可灵的AI模特的时候，很多人问，能不能让模特带首饰？现在，可以了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5612f48f-fae0-44c4-daba-4725d34bd900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1332209106239461\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"593\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186334\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5612f48f-fae0-44c4-daba-4725d34bd900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还用它，直接P图，消除人物。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/16a271d3-7cef-4b42-79bd-e7cb54799c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9762845849802372\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"759\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186336\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/16a271d3-7cef-4b42-79bd-e7cb54799c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">老照片一键修复+上色。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dbc1d9f4-a1f9-4cb6-a52e-9075b39b1400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8349944629014396\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"903\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186337\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dbc1d9f4-a1f9-4cb6-a52e-9075b39b1400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至，还可以模仿字体做自体设计。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e078e9d0-fb6b-4ca1-85c2-7487b142a700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1808510638297873\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"846\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186350\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e078e9d0-fb6b-4ca1-85c2-7487b142a700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在GPT-4o的冲击下，N多的设计师和创业者，都有点emo了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如就有大佬在X上感叹道：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d21f3559-82a5-4882-a44f-5bf1993c9500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6033613445378151\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1190\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186338\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d21f3559-82a5-4882-a44f-5bf1993c9500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">朋友圈里还看到了一张图，是glif的老板，在X上发的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0b416f0a-a5ae-4cd4-15ee-27f9435be500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0527777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186339\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0b416f0a-a5ae-4cd4-15ee-27f9435be500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">纪念ComfyUI，纪念一切的AI图像工作流。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">OpenAI的一次更新，又屠杀了一堆公司。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">又一次深刻的阐明了那句《三体》中的经典台词：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">我消灭你，与你无关。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">GPT-4o的冲击当然是有，但是，他的上限在哪？能做到什么地步？真的能彻底替代ComfyUI的AI图像工作流吗？</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">我想弄清楚这个答案。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">首先我觉得我还是要跟大家非常简单的用一两句话解释一下ComfyUI，让大家知道这玩意是个啥，我们才好继续往下聊。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">ComfyUI是一个非常专业的工作流工具，不局限于AI绘图，AI视频啥的也都可以往里面接。他的界面大概是这样的，很像电路板。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/accd7c2f-e9bd-4490-a016-9efd8741a200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49609375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186343\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/accd7c2f-e9bd-4490-a016-9efd8741a200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">这个就是在Liblib上搭的ComfyUI工作流。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">它是以节点方式，把各个工具、各个模型给串起来，形成一整套的工作流，比如一张图进去，经过各种节点和插件，输出一个完全风格不同的AI视频，这都是OK的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">坦率的讲，我不是ComfyUI的专家的，做过的工作流也不多，我觉得在这个领域，我并没有那么强的发言权，所以。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">我去请教了一下我的1个好朋友，AI绘图大神</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: normal;\">@炼丹师忠忠</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">我想听听，他的看法。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">首先是，GPT-4o对电商设计的冲击到底有多大？</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">我跟忠忠聊了很久。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">最后得到的结论，跟我自己在设计行业里感受到的水温差不多。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对于普通水平的电商设计师，肯定是有打击的，他们原有的技能水平也就只能产出跟gpt4o差不多的图，相对来说意义不大了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上游的运营专员可以自己操作工具来生产一样质量的图。跟被冲击的插画师类似，可能会变为帮忙修补gpt4o产出的图的bug，还有叠加原图部分细节上去加强细节还原（类似于高低频修复流程）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">生产成本降低后，需求量会变大，原本用不起各种华丽背景图包装的商家，现在也用的起了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">从效果上极简操作就能生图的工具有美图设计室等一堆工具，GPT4o只是在某些效果方面更进一步而已，对于专业级的实际商业生产的影响可能没有那么大。</span></span></p>\n  <section>\n   <span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">而从视觉设计角度，对现有的整个开源生态，反而是利好作用。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">忠忠举了自己设计的公司IP的例子。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">现在，可以一句话把IP的3D模型，直出到品牌海报上，不需要走以前的3D建模+渲染了，大大节省了时间。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/60077dc8-6805-47d4-d207-bd1f3b4ee600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8827238335435057\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"793\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186340\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/60077dc8-6805-47d4-d207-bd1f3b4ee600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f2a07d7d-28e6-4472-0341-90d6a9d2e200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7517106549364614\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2046\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186341\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f2a07d7d-28e6-4472-0341-90d6a9d2e200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">同时，更有趣的一点是，GPT-4o可以根据一张IP草图，来生成这个IP的各角度视图。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/19caec9f-1946-4db1-463b-1243fe7d3800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9455782312925171\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2058\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186342\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/19caec9f-1946-4db1-463b-1243fe7d3800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">而这些图，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">会进一步推动flux等开源模型的微调版本的效果。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可能会问，都有GPT-4o了，为什么还要去微调flux，在ComfyUI搭工作流用呢？这不是脱裤子放屁多此一举呢？</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实有两个原因。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">数据隐私性和精准性。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">数据隐私很好解释，就是GPT-4o是一个闭源的模型，后面最多最多也就是开放一个API，让大家接到ComfyUI里面去用，但是，就OpenAI这个尿性，我们给过去的东西，大概率就成他后续的训练素材了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">举个例子，《流浪地球3》2027年上映，要是现在美术组把核心概念图或者设定图直接灌给GPT-4o做一些处理，到时候，《流浪地球3》电影还没上映，设定图你可以直接在GPT-5o里面让它画出来，这特么就炸了。。。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">所以，数据隐私性至关重要，在真正的生产环境里，特别是一些大厂里，必须只能用本地的ComfyUI搭，真正的输出，必须是本地环境，用开源的模型。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">所以，这个时候，我们就可以用一些不敏感的信息，扔给GPT-4o，来辅助生成数据集，反过来微调自己的flux模型，这个点，真的很有用。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">精准性其实也很简单，我们回过头来看忠忠用GPT-4o输出的自己家IP的海报。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ea449fe2-aedb-4e87-9c9c-eb6feb69db00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7518518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186344\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ea449fe2-aedb-4e87-9c9c-eb6feb69db00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">先不说其他的细节了，这几处，你是能发现一些明显的BUG的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">这其实在生产环境里，这种BUG是品牌方觉得不可能接受的，就想你给一个手机产品做广告，你把人手机弄变形了，你跟人说不行AI出得就是这样的，你看对面会不会把你挂在电风扇上转着打。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">而这个时候，用Flux专门微调的Lora，是可以完美的解决这种精准性和一致性的问题的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">这其实就是普通设计场景和专业设计场景的区别。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">GPT-4o当然可以替代大部分的普通工作流，会让ComfyUI里一大批的工作流失去价值，但是这就不代表，ComfyUI失去价值了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">很简单的一点是，在专业的设计工作里，纯对话式的简单界面满足不了复杂专业的需求的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">就像你问一个专业设计师，为什么设计是用PS做设计，而不用美图秀秀来做设计，对方只会把你当傻子。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在真正的专业的AI设计工作里，可控性，很多时候非常的重要。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">需要精确的规定重绘区域，需要精确的调节风格效果，出图尺寸比例等，所以在专业生产中需要精确调节的细节，不能指望OpenAI全做成功能。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47cb8bbe-3c51-4a57-f253-ade462c78600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186345\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/47cb8bbe-3c51-4a57-f253-ade462c78600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有前后处理流程，比如说前置的裁剪，抠图，语义识别，后置的比如对图片的放大，贴回原图细节（高低频修复），再接入其他工作流继续处理等。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">自动化一键完成的效率要比多轮对话高很多。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">包括在一些精准度要求高的产品和场景上，GPT-4o目前还达不到专业级的水准。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看个例子。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我们要把问界M9这款车，换到另一个场景里。车这种产品，跟笔、戒指、香水等等要求的精细度，完全不一样。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ff2d3003-c638-422d-530d-b080d1b13800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7660044150110376\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1812\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186346\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ff2d3003-c638-422d-530d-b080d1b13800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是GPT-4o出的图。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/56cba15d-c8ec-4d44-867b-a05b284b2e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186347\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/56cba15d-c8ec-4d44-867b-a05b284b2e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而如果我们用大佬的牛逼工作流呢？</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a5202e29-1d1f-4215-d23e-f017b0cb0400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49609375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186348\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a5202e29-1d1f-4215-d23e-f017b0cb0400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">生成出来的效果在整体比例和质感上，是更好的。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/234a589d-3e2d-4beb-c0f7-ba8830451d00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.52265625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500186349\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/234a589d-3e2d-4beb-c0f7-ba8830451d00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对比应该非常直观了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这里我要给自己叠个甲，我并不是在这里鼓吹，GPT-4o不行，ComfyUI的效果可以吊打GPT-4o。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果是这样的话，我也不会连更两篇，来给大家看一看，GPT-4o，有多酷，有多强。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我想说的是，GPT-4o，跟当年的SD、Midjorney、Runway、可灵等等AI工具是一样的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">会无差别替代所有这个行业里面的初级执行职位。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">屠杀所有曾经在工程层面对大模型进行的一些优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，一点一点侵蚀更上层的建筑。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它更像是一层层汹涌上涨的潮水，将整个AI图像领域原有的边界打得支离破碎。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">都说做AI产品，要看到大模型的边界，在边界之外的安全地带做。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是现在，你根本不知道边界在何方。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那些看似高耸的技术壁垒与工作流程，如果只是基于简单组装或者初级执行的逻辑，正在被GPT-4o以近乎暴力的方式消解。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">绝大多数机械式的制作工作，一旦被强大的多模态理解与生成替代，就会像那些轰然倒塌的围墙一样，被历史的风尘轻易覆盖。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">有没有一种第一次工业革命时候，机器代替手工劳动的即视感？</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3f05c67d-3e5d-404f-b348-91c129852100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5542763157894737\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"608\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"320\" data-imgfileid=\"500186351\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3f05c67d-3e5d-404f-b348-91c129852100/public\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">历史总是在不断的重复。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可一如上文所言，这绝不代表ComfyUI之流就会被完全淘汰。&nbsp;</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在工业级、专业级的深度工作流里，人们对数据安全、设计精度、可控度的需求不可能凭空消失。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那种图像与视频的多次处理、分层输出、版本管理、脚本化批量运行、自动化节点衔接，只要是大型企业或核心团队，都会很在意。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GPT-4o会在C端和中小B端市场里摧枯拉朽，取代了大量低端或者重复性工作。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而ComfyUI、Flux、ControlNet等开源生态则在更专业的领域继续进化，利用它们精细、可控、可离线部署的特性，为高端客户或机密项目提供服务。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这气势就像云端办公与本地办公的关系一样，前者无限便捷，后者安全可控。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也如同家用轿车与顶级跑车的分别，各自目标用户并不冲突。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GPT-4o也一定会不断进化，去扩大自己的边界蚕食更多的场景。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">开源生态也会有各种可以复刻效果的模型、产品出来，从而进行私有化。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没什么能够阻止浪潮向前。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">要么成为浪潮的追随者，要么成为浪潮的推手。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这二者，都肯定比做一块沉在海底的礁石，要精彩得多。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你说是吗。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n  <section>\n   <span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;U6jJdjKqroJkAvxoRATcwWMMn6L&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;会进一步推动flux等开源模型的微调版本的效果，这个角度上讲是利好于ComfyUI的应用的，效果越好，用的人越多。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+1l&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7369895764597669889&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:false,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;91000d6a-5f27-475c-9e78-6f301395e1ca&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:16,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:100,&quot;end&quot;:157},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;YWH6dX1eioJumcx2aiVcrdU6nge&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "GPT-4o 多模态生图对电商设计产生冲击，降低了入门门槛，但数据安全、设计精度和可控度等专业需求仍需 ComfyUI 等工具满足。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "GPT-4o 多模态生图对电商设计产生冲击，降低了入门门槛，但数据安全、设计精度和可控度等专业需求仍需 ComfyUI 等工具满足。",
